#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn48.68"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn48.68:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.68:0.2"
msgid "7. Bodhipakkhiyavagga "
msgstr "7. Leading to Awakening "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn48.68:0.3"
msgid "68. Dutiyarukkhasutta "
msgstr "68. A Tree (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.238, sc1
msgctxt "sn48.68:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci devānaṃ tāvatiṃsānaṃ rukkhā, pārichattako tesaṃ aggamakkhāyati; "
msgstr "“Mendicants, of all the trees belonging to the gods of the Thirty-Three, the Shady Orchid Tree is said to be the best. "

msgctxt "sn48.68:1.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, ye keci bodhipakkhiyā dhammā, paññindriyaṃ tesaṃ aggamakkhāyati, yadidaṃ—bodhāya. "
msgstr "In the same way, the faculty of wisdom is said to be the best of the qualities that lead to awakening in terms of becoming awakened. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.68:1.3"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, bodhipakkhiyā dhammā? "
msgstr "And what are the qualities that lead to awakening? "

msgctxt "sn48.68:1.4"
msgid "Saddhindriyaṃ, bhikkhave, bodhipakkhiyo dhammo, taṃ bodhāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "The faculties of faith, "

msgctxt "sn48.68:1.5"
msgid "Vīriyindriyaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "energy, "

msgctxt "sn48.68:1.6"
msgid "satindriyaṃ … "
msgstr "mindfulness, "

msgctxt "sn48.68:1.7"
msgid "samādhindriyaṃ … "
msgstr "immersion, "

msgctxt "sn48.68:1.8"
msgid "paññindriyaṃ bodhipakkhiyo dhammo, taṃ bodhāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "and wisdom are qualities that lead to awakening, in that they lead to becoming awakened. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.68:1.9"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci devānaṃ tāvatiṃsānaṃ rukkhā, pārichattako tesaṃ aggamakkhāyati; "
msgstr "Of all the trees belonging to the gods of the Thirty-Three, the shady orchid tree is said to be the best. "

msgctxt "sn48.68:1.10"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, ye keci bodhipakkhiyā dhammā, paññindriyaṃ tesaṃ aggamakkhāyati, yadidaṃ—bodhāyā”ti. "
msgstr "In the same way, the faculty of wisdom is said to be the best of the qualities that lead to awakening in terms of becoming awakened.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.68:1.11"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

